OL,3,CCity falls silent to honour 37th
OL,4,Canniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,5,Cdisaster
OL,7,FLiverpool's city centre fell silent to
OL,8,Fmark 37 years since the Hillsborough
OL,9,Fdisaster.
OL,11,FThe tribute was held at 15:06 BST, the
OL,12,Fexact time the FA Cup semi-final
OL,13,Ffootball match was stopped.
OL,15,FThe disaster saw 97 Liverpool fans
OL,16,Funlawfully killed on 15 April 1989, as
OL,17,Fa result of a crush at the
OL,18,FHillsborough Stadium in Sheffield
OL,19,Fduring the match between Liverpool and
OL,20,FNottingham Forest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
