OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776287489
OL,3,CCity falls silent to honour 37th
OL,4,Canniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,5,Cdisaster
OL,7,FFollowing the silence, a bell tolled
OL,8,F97 times in tribute to each individual
OL,9,Fvictim followed by an instrumental
OL,10,Fversion of You'll Never Walk Alone.
OL,12,FThe tribute was led by the Lord Mayor
OL,13,Fof Liverpool Cllr Barbara Murray and
OL,14,FLiverpool City Council leader Liam
OL,15,FRobinson.
OL,17,FMembers of the public also gathered to
OL,18,Fpay their respects.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776287489
OL,3,CCity falls silent to honour 37th
OL,4,Canniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,5,Cdisaster
OL,7,FAcross the city, flags were at half
OL,8,Fmast from all civic buildings and the
OL,9,FTown Hall is set to be lit up red in
OL,10,Fthe evening.
OL,12,FAt Anfield, 97 balloons were released
OL,13,Ffrom the stadium's centre-circle.
OL,15,FLiverpool's head coach Arne Slot led
OL,16,Ftributes at the club's grounds where
OL,17,Fhe lay a wreath at the Hillsborough
OL,18,FMemorial.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
