OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776287489
OL,3,CCity falls silent to honour 37th
OL,4,Canniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,5,Cdisaster
OL,7,FHe was joined by the Reds' men's
OL,8,Fcaptain Virgil Van Dijk and women's
OL,9,Fcaptain Grace Fisk, along with senior
OL,10,Fclub officials.
OL,12,FIn a statement Liverpool FC paid
OL,13,Ftribute to the 97 supporters on what
OL,14,Fit said is "a poignant day".
OL,16,FIt said: "Ninety-seven children, women
OL,17,Fand men lost their lives as a result
OL,18,Fof the events that occurred at the
OL,19,FReds' FA Cup semi-final against
OL,20,FNottingham Forest on April 15, 1989.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776287489
OL,3,CCity falls silent to honour 37th
OL,4,Canniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,5,Cdisaster
OL,7,F"Ever since, the bereaved families and
OL,8,Fsurvivors of the tragedy have
OL,9,Fdemonstrated remarkable courage,
OL,10,Fdignity and resilience in search of
OL,11,Ftruth and justice.
OL,13,F"In April 2016, an inquest jury
OL,14,Fconcluded that each of the
OL,15,FHillsborough victims had been
OL,16,Funlawfully killed and that no role was
OL,17,Fplayed by fans in causing the disaster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776287489
OL,3,CCity falls silent to honour 37th
OL,4,Canniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,5,Cdisaster
OL,7,F"Our thoughts on this significant and
OL,8,Fpoignant day, as always, are with all
OL,9,Fthose affected by the tragedy at
OL,10,FHillsborough and we pause in memory of
OL,11,Fthe 97 fans who will never be
OL,12,Fforgotten."
OL,14,FAt Everton's new Hill Dickinson
OL,15,FStadium a permanent memorial plaque
OL,16,Fwas unveiled by the club in solidarity
OL,17,Fwith Liverpool FC, which paid respect
OL,18,Fto the 97 victims.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776287489
OL,3,CCity falls silent to honour 37th
OL,4,Canniversary of the Hillsborough
OL,5,Cdisaster
OL,7,FEverton CEO Angus Kinnear was joined
OL,8,Fby representatives of the Hillsborough
OL,9,Ffamilies Margaret Aspinall, Sue
OL,10,FRoberts, Charlotte Hennessey and
OL,11,FStephen Kelly as wreaths were laid at
OL,12,Fthe memorial.
OL,14,FThe Labour Government vowed to
OL,15,Fintroduce a Hillsborough Law in their
OL,16,F2024 manifesto, which would require
OL,17,Fpublic officials to tell the truth
OL,18,Fduring inquiries and investigations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
